    "title": "Hiring Store Manager at Starbucks India International Enterprises",
    "description": "Grow your career with Starbucks India International Enterprises! We are hiring a Store Manager for our Ludhiana team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Starbucks India International Enterprises:\nStarbucks India International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Starbucks India International Enterprises!",
